-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <April 3, 2023> -- Description: <Procedure to search attendances> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[BuscarAsistenciasId] @Idpersonal int AS BEGIN SELECT * FROM Asistencias WHERE Id_personal = @Idpersonal AND Asistencias.Estado = 'ENTRADA' END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[BuscarCargos] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO
-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <Create Date,,> -- Description: <Procedure to search a position> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[BuscarCargos] @Buscador VARCHAR(50) AS BEGIN SELECT Id_cargo, Cargo, SueldoPorHora AS [Sueldo Por Hora] FROM Cargo WHERE Cargo LIKE '%' + @Buscador + '%' END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[BuscarPersonal] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO
-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <Create Date,,> -- Description: <Procedure for looking for users> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[BuscarPersonal] @Desde int, @Hasta int, @Buscador VARCHAR(50) AS BEGIN SET NOCOUNT ON; SELECT Id_personal, Nombres, Identificacion, SueldoPorHora, Cargo, Id_cargo, Estado, codigo, Pais FROM (SELECT Id_personal, Nombres, Identificacion, Personal.SueldoPorHora, Cargo.Cargo, Personal.Id_cargo, Estado, codigo, Pais, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY Id_personal) 'Numero_de_fila' FROM Personal INNER JOIN Cargo ON Cargo.Id_cargo = Personal.Id_cargo) AS Paginado WHERE (Paginado.Numero_de_fila >= @Desde) AND (Paginado.Numero_de_fila <= @Hasta) AND (Nombres + Identificacion LIKE '%' + @Buscador + '%') END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[BuscarPersonalIdentidad] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO

-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <April 16, 2023> -- Description: <Procedure to confirm a checkout> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[ConfirmarSalida] @Id_personal int, @Fecha_salida DATETIME, @Horas NUMERIC(18,2) AS BEGIN UPDATE Asistencias SET Fecha_salida = @Fecha_salida, Horas = @Horas, Estado = 'SALIDA' WHERE Id_personal = @Id_personal AND Estado = 'ENTRADA' END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[EditarCargo] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO
-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <Create Date,,> -- Description: <Procedure to edit a position> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[EditarCargo] @Id_cargo int, @Cargo VARCHAR(MAX), @SueldoPorHora NUMERIC(12,8) AS BEGIN IF EXISTS (SELECT Cargo FROM Cargo WHERE Cargo = @Cargo AND Id_cargo <> @Id_cargo) RAISERROR ('Ya existe un cargo con este nombre', 16, 1) ELSE UPDATE Cargo SET Cargo = @Cargo, SueldoPorHora = @SueldoPorHora WHERE Id_cargo = @Id_cargo END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[EditarPersonal] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO -- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <Create Date,,> -- Description: <Procedure to edit a user> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[EditarPersonal] @Id_personal int, @Nombres VARCHAR(MAX), @Identificacion VARCHAR(MAX), @Pais VARCHAR(MAX), @Id_cargo int, @Sueldo_Por_Hora numeric(18,2) AS BEGIN IF EXISTS (SELECT Identificacion FROM Personal WHERE Identificacion = @Identificacion AND Id_personal <> @Id_personal) RAISERROR ('Ya existe un registro con esta identifiación', 16, 1) ELSE UPDATE Personal SET Nombres = @Nombres, Identificacion = @Identificacion, Pais = @Pais, Id_cargo = @Id_cargo, SueldoPorHora = @Sueldo_Por_Hora WHERE Id_personal = @Id_personal END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[EliminarPermisos] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO

-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <Create Date,,> -- Description: <Procedure to insert a user> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[InsertarPersonal] @Nombres VARCHAR(MAX), @Identificacion VARCHAR(MAX), @Pais VARCHAR(MAX), @Id_cargo int, @SueldoPorHora numeric(18,2) AS BEGIN DECLARE @Estado VARCHAR(MAX) DECLARE @codigo VARCHAR(MAX) DECLARE @Id_personal int SET @Estado = 'ACTIVO' SET @codigo = '-'
IF EXISTS (SELECT Identificacion FROM Personal WHERE Identificacion = @Identificacion) RAISERROR ('Ya existe un registro con esta identificación', 16, 1) ELSE INSERT INTO Personal VALUES ( @Nombres, @Identificacion, @Pais, @Id_cargo, @SueldoPorHora, @Estado, @codigo ) SELECT @Id_personal = scope_identity() UPDATE Personal SET codigo = @Id_personal WHERE Id_personal = @Id_personal END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[InsertarUsuario] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO
-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <April 23, 2023> -- Description: <Procedure to insert a user> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[InsertarUsuario] @Nombres VARCHAR(50), @Login VARCHAR(50), @Password VARCHAR(50), @Icono image, @Estado VARCHAR(50) AS BEGIN IF EXISTS (SELECT Login FROM Usuarios WHERE Login = @Login) RAISERROR ('Ya existe un registro con ese usuario', 16, 1) ELSE INSERT INTO Usuarios VALUES ( @Nombres, @Login, @Password, @Icono, @Estado ) END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[MostrarPermisos] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO
-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <April 23, 2023> -- Description: <Procedure for showing the permissions> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[MostrarPermisos] @idUsuario int AS BEGIN SELECT IdModulo FROM Permisos WHERE IdUsuario = @idUsuario END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[MostrarPersonal] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO
-- ============================================= -- Author: <Vivian Munguía> -- Create date: <Create Date,,> -- Description: <Procedure for showing the users> -- ============================================= CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[MostrarPersonal] @Desde int, @Hasta int AS BEGIN SET NOCOUNT ON; SELECT Id_personal, Nombres, Identificacion, SueldoPorHora, Cargo, Id_cargo, Estado, codigo, Pais FROM (SELECT Id_personal, Nombres, Identificacion, Personal.SueldoPorHora, Cargo.Cargo, Personal.Id_cargo, Estado, codigo, Pais, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY Id_personal) 'Numero_de_fila' FROM Personal INNER JOIN Cargo ON Cargo.Id_cargo = Personal.Id_cargo) AS Paginado WHERE (Paginado.Numero_de_fila >= @Desde) AND (Paginado.Numero_de_fila <= @Hasta) END GO /****** Object: StoredProcedure [dbo].[RestaurarPersonal] Script Date: 30/04/2023 05:27:30 p. m. ******/ SET ANSI_NULLS ON GO SET QUOTED_IDENTIFIER ON GO
